M|Use |tx|Mark frequent, non-ur state updates as transitions to maintain UI responsiveness.
M|Use |**In|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|fn ScrollTracker() {
M|Use |tx|const [scrollY, setScrollY] = useState(0)
M|Use |tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Use |tx|const handler = () => setScrollY(window.scrollY)
M|Use |wind|true })
M|Use |tx|return () => window.removeEventListener('scroll', handler)
M|Use |tx|}, [])
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
